[[2003年大西洋飓风季|2003年大西洋飓风季]]是一次较为活跃的[[大西洋飓风季|大西洋飓风季]]，于美国时间2003年6月1日正式开始，同年11月30日结束，传统上这样的日期界定了一年中绝大多数[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]在[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]形成的时间段<ref name = "AOML FAQ G1">{{cite web | author = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory, Hurricane Research Division | title = Frequently Asked Questions: When is hurricane season? | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | accessdate = 2014-05-31 | archivedate = 2014-03-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325071130/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/G1.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/G1.html }}</ref><ref name="61two">{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | year = 2003 | title = June 1 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，但本次飓风季无论是在正式时间段之前和之后都存在热带天气系统活动，[[2003年热带风暴安娜|热带风暴安娜]]早在4月20日开始形成，这时离飓风季正式开始还有超过40天的时间，全年的风暴活动一直持续到了12月11日。

本季是有纪录以来最活跃的大西洋飓风季之一，共计产生21个热带低气压，其中16个达到热带风暴强度并因此获得命名，7个达到飓风强度，3场成为大型飓风，还有1场达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下最高的[[五级大西洋飓风列表|五级]]强度<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150406161442/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-022315.txt | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-022315.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2015-03-02 | accessdate = 2015-04-07 | archivedate = 2015-04-06 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = NHC Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track ("HURDAT") | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA) | date = 2006-02-17 | accessdate = 2014-05-31 | archivedate = 2013-10-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029213935/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/tracks1851to2007-apr08.txt | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/tracks1851to2007-apr08.txt }}</ref>。全季最具影响的风暴分别是[[飓风法比安|飓风法比安]]、[[飓风伊莎贝尔|伊莎贝尔]]和[[飓风胡安|胡安]]，其名称也因飓风造成的严重破坏而退役<ref name="2003wmo">{{cite web | author = World Meteorological Organization | year = 2004 | title = Final Report of the Twenty-Sixth Session | accessdate = 2008-05-28 | url = http://www.wmo.ch/pages/prog/www/TCP_vO/Meetings/HC-26/doc14.doc | format = DOC | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080528184100/http://www.wmo.ch/pages/prog/www/TCP_vO/Meetings/HC-26/doc14.doc | archivedate = 2008-05-28 }}</ref>。飓风季期间的所有风暴一共夺走至少92条人命，还造成44亿美元的破坏。
