|1-min winds=30
|Pressure=1008
}}
6月6日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]{{#tag:ref|[[东风波|东风波]]指的是沿[[信风|信风]]移动的倒置[[低压槽|低压槽]]<ref name="gloss">{{cite report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-03-25 | accessdate = 2015-03-27 | title = Glossary of NHC Terms | archivedate = 2014-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140601020814/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml }}</ref>。|group="注"}}离开非洲海岸<ref name="td2tcr">{{cite web | last = Franklin | first = James | date = 2003-08-06 | title = Tropical Depression Two Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2010-11-29 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003two.shtml? | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-05-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140527220631/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003two.shtml }}</ref>。系统在低[[纬度|纬度]]海域向西移动，其轴线上存在的扰动天气到6月9日时组织结构已有改善<ref>{{cite report | last = Lawrence | first = Miles | date = 2003-06-09 | title = June 9 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，考虑到此时飓风季尚未开始，系统的外境环境相对而言已很有利于热带气旋发展。系统起初没有层次分明的下层[[大气环流|环流]]<ref>{{cite report | last = Franklin | first = James | date = 2003-06-09 | title = June 9 Tropical Weather Outlook (2) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，6月10日，对流已有进一步增长，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]于6月11日清晨宣布位于热带大西洋中部的气旋已成为第二号热带低气压<ref name="td2tcr" /><ref name="td2disc1">{{cite web | last = Avila | first = Lixion | date = 2003-06-11 | title = Tropical Depression Two Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-04-06 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al022003.discus.001.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812111041/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al022003.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-12 }}</ref>，这也是有纪录以来第4个于6月在[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]以东发展形成的热带气旋<ref name="June 03" />，另外两个分别是[[2000年大西洋飓风季#第二号热带低气压|2000年的第二号热带低气压]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2000/summ0006.htm | title = Monthly Global Tropical Cyclone Summary June 2000 | author = Padgett, Gary | year = 2000 | publisher = Australia Severe Weather | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141218103234/http://australiasevereweather.com/cyclones/2000/summ0006.htm | accessdate = 2015-04-06 | archivedate = 2014-12-18 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，1979年的[[1979年大西洋飓风季#热带风暴安娜|热带风暴安娜]]，以及[[1933年大西洋飓风季#第二号飓风|1933年的第二号飓风]]<ref name="June 03">{{cite web | author = Pasch, Richard / Stewart, Stacy / Lawrence, Miles | date = 2003-07-01 | title = June 2003 Tropical Weather Summary | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-04-06 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/tws/MIATWSAT_jun.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812110936/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/tws/MIATWSAT_jun.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-12 }}</ref>。

气象部门起初预测低气压会达到热带风暴标准，并在周围保有良好的[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]和部分[[雨带|带状特征]]<ref name="td2disc1" />。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]6月11日上午9点左右，根据卫星数据估计，低气压的强度已接近热带风暴标准<ref name="td2disc2">{{cite web | last = Pasch | first = Richard | date = 2003-06-11 | title = Tropical Depression Two Discussion Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-04-06 | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812110940/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al022003.discus.002.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al022003.discus.002.shtml? }}</ref>。但是，系统中的对流随后就开始消亡并移位至中心的东北方向，低气压也于6月11日晚在[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]东南偏东方向约1535公里海域退化成东风波<ref name="td2tcr" />。虽然东风波的组织结构依然良好，并带有层次分明的下层涡旋，但由于存在强烈的风切变而无法得到发展<ref>{{cite report | last = Formosa | first = Mike | date = 2003-06-13 | title = June 13 Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。6月13日，系统残留经过小安的列斯群岛，并继续向西穿越[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]<ref>{{cite report | last = Avila | first = Lixion | date = 2003-06-13 | title = June 13 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。
