{{Main|2003年热带风暴比尔}}
热带风暴比尔源于6月29日[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]以北的一股东风波。系统在北上期间缓慢增强，并在从[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[泰勒博恩堂区_(路易斯安那州)|泰勒博恩堂区]][[肖万_(路易斯安那州)|肖万]]（{{lang|en|Chauvin}}）以西约43公里处[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]前不久达到风力时速95公里的最高强度。比尔在陆地上空迅速减弱并加速向东北进发，风暴带来的湿气与逐渐逼近[[冷锋|冷锋]]中的冷空气结合，催生出多达34场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]。7月2日，风暴转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，并在当天晚些时候被冷锋吸收而消散<ref name="billtcr">{{cite web | last = Avila | first = Lixion | year = 2003 | title = Tropical Storm Bill Tropical Cyclone Report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714231236/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003bill.shtml | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003bill.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

风暴在登陆[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]期间产生中等强度[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]，引发[[潮汐|潮汐]][[洪灾|洪灾]]<ref name="ncdcla">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2003 | title = Event Report for Louisiana | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。该州东北部一个小镇的[[堤|堤防]]遭大浪突破，镇上许多民房被淹<ref name="lasurge">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2003 | title = Event Report for Louisiana (2) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。[[土壤|土壤]]湿软加上中等强度的大风导致许多树木倒塌，有些还砸中了房屋和供电线路<ref name="billnws">{{cite web | author = New Orleans National Weather Service | year = 2003 | title = Tropical Storm Bill Post Tropical Cyclone Report | accessdate = 2006-10-22 | url = http://www.srh.weather.gov/lix/html/psh_bill.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081204024056/http://www.srh.weather.gov/lix/html/psh_bill.htm | archivedate = 2008-12-04 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，引起数十万用户失去电力供应<ref name="billusatoday">{{cite news | author = Associated Press | title = Gulf Coast reeling from Tropical Storm Bill | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017105247/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/news/2003-06-30-gulfcoast-bill_x.htm | accessdate = 2014-06-09 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/news/2003-06-30-gulfcoast-bill_x.htm | work = USA Today | date = 2003-07-03 | archivedate = 2012-10-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴在更为内陆的区域催生出多场龙卷风，局部地区受到中等程度破坏。热带风暴比尔行经之处共计夺走了4条人命，造成的经济损失约为5000万美元（2003[[美元|美元]]，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|50000000|2003}}}}美元）<ref name="billtcr"/>。
