7月14日，一股东风波离开非洲西海岸<ref name="td6tcr">{{cite web | last = Lawrence | first = Miles | date = 2003-08-18 | title = Tropical Depression Six Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002000056/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003six.shtml | accessdate = 2013-10-02 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003six.shtml | archivedate = 2013-10-02 }}</ref>。系统起初稳步向西移动，并随着上层气流环境变得更加有利而发展出较为集中的[[雷暴|雷暴]]<ref>{{cite report | last = Avila | first = Lixion | date = 2003-07-19 | title = July 19 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，美国国家飓风中心于7月19日晚把位于小安的列斯群岛以东约1675公里海域的系统归类为第六号热带低气压<ref name="td6tcr" />。成为热带气旋后，低气压的北侧和南翼均保有结构混乱的钩状雨带，气象部门起初认为，由于水温较高，风切变非常少，[[快速增强|爆发性增强]]所需要的5项条件已经达成4项，因此气旋会在达到飓风强度后穿越小安的列斯群岛<ref name="td6disc1">{{cite web | last = Avila | first = Lixion | date = 2003-07-19 | title = Tropical Depression Six Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-04-06 | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812110853/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al062003.discus.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al062003.discus.001.shtml? }}</ref>。但接下来由于冷空气入侵，并且东南方向还有扰动天气造成系统不稳定，低气压的对流因此消亡<ref>{{cite web | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | date = 2003-06-20 | title = Tropical Depression Six Discussion Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812110933/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al062003.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-04-06 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al062003.discus.003.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-08-12 }}</ref>。

由于系统的移动速度很快，气象部门在7月20日这天已很难确认下层环流的存在<ref>{{cite web | last = Lawrence | first = Miles | date = 2003-07-20 | title = Tropical Depression Six Discussion Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-04-06 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al062003.discus.004.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150213065355/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al062003.discus.004.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-02-13 }}</ref>。7月21日，弧形对流有所增长<ref>{{cite web | last = Beven | first = Jack | date = 2003-07-21 | title = Tropical Depression Six Discussion Six | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-04-06 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al062003.discus.006.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-02-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150213055557/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al062003.discus.006.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>，小安的列斯群岛中的多个岛屿为此发布[[熱帶氣旋警告|热带风暴警告或观察预警]]。经过巴巴多斯以北洋面后，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]][[侦察机|侦察机]]未能在系统内找到闭合下层环流，美国国家飓风中心因此估计低气压已于7月21日晚退化成开放式东风波。系统残留给小安的列斯群岛带去少量降水<ref name="td6tcr" />，之后进入加勒比海，但由于风切变增多而无法重新发展<ref>{{cite report | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | date = 2003-07-22 | title = July 22 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。东风波的北部在与南部分裂后发展成为第七号热带低气压<ref name="td6tcr" />。
