7月23日，有东风波与上层[[低气压|低气压]]相互作用，在[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]附近发展出深层对流区<ref name="td7tcr">{{cite web | last = Pasch | first = Richard | date = 2003-11-30 | title = Tropical Depression Seven Tropical Cyclone Report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140330143924/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003seven.shtml | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-20 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003seven.shtml | archivedate = 2014-03-30 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。系统总体向西北偏北方向前进，其中发展出中到下层环流，美国国家飓风中心根据地面和卫星观测数量估计系统于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}7月25日中午12点在佛罗里达州[[戴通纳海滩|戴通纳海滩]]以东约95公里海域发展成第七号热带低气压。系统所受环境由[[高气压|高气压]]占主导地位，行经洋面水温较低<ref name="td7tcr" />，同时还受到不利的上层风影响，所以风力时速始终未能超过55公里<ref>{{cite web | last = Avila | first = Lixion | date = 2003-07-25 | title = Tropical Depression Seven Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-04-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812110914/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al072003.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al072003.discus.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-08-12 }}</ref>。

7月26日清晨，低气压登陆[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]][[圣凯瑟琳岛|圣凯瑟琳岛]]（{{lang|en|St. Catherines Island}}），然后在陆地上空逐渐减弱，于7月27日消散。气象部门从未预测系统会达到热带风暴强度，所以也就没有发布任何热带风暴警告或观察预警。<ref name="td7tcr" />不过乔治亚州和[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]大部分地区都发布了洪灾预警<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.news4jax.com/news4georgia/2358185/detail.html | title = Saturday: No. 7 Unlucky For Soggy Georgia, SC | date = 2003-07-26 | publisher = WJXT | accessdate = 2011-09-27 | archivedate = 2011-09-27 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110927152340/http://www.news4jax.com/news4georgia/2358185/detail.html }}</ref>。佛罗里达州到[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]沿海地区出现小到中雨，其中以乔治亚州的[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]降雨量最高，有131毫米。大部分地区的降雨量在25到76毫米之间<ref>{{cite web | last = Roth | first = David | date = 2008-08-04 | title = Tropical Depression #7 - July 25-27, 2003 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2015-04-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141221185338/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td72003.html | archivedate = 2014-12-21 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td72003.html }}</ref>。没有任何报道表明低气压有造成任何破坏或人员伤亡<ref name="td7tcr" />。
