{{main|2003年第九号热带低气压}}
8月14日，一股强烈的[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲海岸<ref name="td9tcr">{{cite web | last = Avila | first = Lixion | date = 2003-11-17 | title = Tropical Depression Nine Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002000123/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003nine.shtml | accessdate = 2010-11-29 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003nine.shtml? | archivedate = 2013-10-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>稳步向西移动，于8月18日组织出良好的对流区<ref name="aug18two2">{{cite report | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | date = 2003-08-18 | title = August 18 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。系统经过小安的列斯群岛，然后于8月21日在[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]以南海域发展成第九号热带低气压。低气压很快显示出组织迹象，气象学家预计系统会发展成强烈热带风暴<ref name="td9disc1">{{cite web | last = Avila | first = Lixion | date = 2003-08-21 | title = Tropical Depression Nine Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812111044/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al092003.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2010-11-29 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al092003.discus.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-08-12 }}</ref>。但是，系统上空意外出现强烈的西南向风切变，导致热带低气压于8月22日晚在多明尼加最东端以南洋面退化成东风波<ref name="td9tcr" />。

低气压的残留给多明尼加共和国带去小到中雨，引发洪灾和河流泛滥，有上百套房屋被淹，还有农作物受损<ref name="2003wmo" />。该国当时已遭受持续数月的干旱，风暴带来的降水缓解了旱情<ref name="domrep">{{cite web | author = stormCARIB | accessdate = 2015-04-07 | url = http://www.stormcarib.com/reports/2003/domrep.shtml | year = 2003 | title = Unofficial Reports from the Dominican Republic | archivedate = 2015-02-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150213032529/http://www.stormcarib.com/reports/2003/domrep.shtml }}</ref>。[[牙买加|牙买加]]东部也出现洪灾，但经受的损失程度不明<ref name="2003wmo" />。
