{{main|2003年热带风暴格雷斯}}
8月19日，一股强劲东风波伴随低气压系统离开非洲海岸快速向西移动，这此期间没有显著发展，于8月29日在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]发展出低气压区。对流继续组织，东风波于8月30日在德克萨斯州[[科珀斯克里斯蒂_(得克萨斯州)|科珀斯克里斯蒂]]东南偏东方向约540公里洋面发展成第十一号热带低气压。低气压迅速增强成热带风暴格雷斯，但由于附近的上层低气压影响而无法进一步强化。8月31日，格雷斯从德克萨斯州[[加尔维斯顿岛|加尔维斯顿岛]]登陆，在陆地上区快速弱化。风暴转向东北，于9月2日在[[俄克拉何马州|俄克拉何马州]]最东面被[[冷锋|冷锋]]吸收<ref name="gracetcr">{{cite web | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | date = 2003-11-27 | title = Tropical Storm Grace Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-04-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003grace.shtml | archivedate = 2013-10-02 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002000141/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003grace.shtml }}</ref>。

受风暴影响，德克萨斯州到[[美国东部|美国东部]]普降小到中雨，其中又以德克萨斯州东部降雨量最高，达263毫米<ref name="gracerain">{{cite web | author = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2005 | title = Rainfall data for Tropical Storm Grace | accessdate = 2015-04-07 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/grace2003.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141221185402/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/grace2003.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-12-21 }}</ref>。格雷斯登陆前就导致低洼地区被淹，还造成轻度海滩侵蚀<ref name="jambeach">{{cite web | author = Jim O'Donnel | year = 2003 | title = Tropical Storm Grace Preliminary Storm Report | publisher = Jamaica Beach Weather Observatory | accessdate = 2008-07-05 | archivedate = 2008-07-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080705193935/http://members.aol.com/IslandWx/jbclimo/tropicalcyclone/reports/2003/grace.htm | url = http://members.aol.com/IslandWx/jbclimo/tropicalcyclone/reports/2003/grace.htm }}</ref>。风暴残留令俄克拉何马州和[[密苏里州|密苏里州]]南部出现局部洪灾<ref name="oklanws">{{cite web | author = Ty Judd | year = 2003 | title = The 2003 Labor Day Weekend Heavy Rain and Flooding Event | publisher = Norman, Oklahoma National Weather Service | accessdate = 2006-08-18 | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/oun/newsletter/autumn2003/ | archivedate = 2007-06-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070619052549/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/oun/newsletter/autumn2003/ }}</ref><ref name="paducnws">{{cite web | author = Paducah, Kentucky National Weather Service | year = 2003 | title = Autumn 2003 Weather Summary | accessdate = 2006-08-18 | url = http://www.crh.noaa.gov/pah/climate/autumn03.php | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120805202102/http://www.crh.noaa.gov/pah/climate/autumn03.php | archivedate = 2012-08-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。没有报道表明格雷斯有造成人员丧生，并且总体破坏程度也很轻微<ref name="gracetcr" />。
