{{Main|2003年热带风暴亨利}}
8月22日，一股东风波离开非洲海岸，其结构杂乱无章，于9月1日进入墨西哥湾东部。9月3日，有[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]在佛罗里达州[[坦帕_(佛罗里达州)|坦帕]]以西约480公里洋面发展成第十二号热带低气压。系统向东移动，于9月5日升级成热带风暴并获名“亨利”（{{lang|en|Henri}}），虽然受强烈风切变影响，但风暴还是在当天晚上达到持续风速每小时95公里的最高强度。气旋随后迅速减弱，以热带低气压强度袭击佛罗里达州西海岸。9月8日，低气压在北卡罗莱纳州近海退化成残留低气压区<ref name="henritcr">{{cite web | author = Daniel P. Brown and Miles Lawrence | year = 2003 | title = Tropical Storm Henri Tropical Cyclone Report | deadurl = yes | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003henri.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714135311/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003henri.shtml | archivedate = 2014-07-14 }}</ref>，然后从[[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）附近登岸<ref name="two12">{{cite report | author = James L. Franklin | year = 2003 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook for September 12, 2003 | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，系统穿越中大西洋地区，最终于9月17日在[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]上空消散<ref name="wpc">{{cite web | author = David Roth | year = 2006 | title = Rainfall information on Tropical Storm Henri | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2013-11-03 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/henri2003.html | archivedate = 2013-09-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130922044322/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/henri2003.html }}</ref>。

受亨利影响，佛罗里达州多地有局部暴雨，但造成的破坏程度很轻<ref name="henritcr" />。风暴残留给[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]和[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]]带去强降水，造成价值1960万美元（2003年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|19000000|2003}}}}美元）的破坏<ref name="dedam">{{cite web | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2003 | title = Event Report for Delaware | accessdate = 2007-12-19 | archivedate = 2012-01-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120112203406/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~489038 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~489038 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref name="pedam">{{cite web | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2003 | title = Event Report for Pennsylvania | accessdate = 2012-01-12 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~513663 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120112203411/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~513663 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-01-12 }}</ref>。特拉华州的河流洪灾创下新纪录，红土溪（{{lang|en|Red Clay Creek}}）部分河段洪水属500年一遇水平<ref name="deriv">{{cite web |author=Stefanie Baxter |year=2003 |title=Henri Visits Delaware |publisher=Delaware Geological Survey |accessdate=2013-11-03 |archivedate=2011-09-28 |deadurl=yes |url=http://ag.udel.edu/dwrc/newsletters/Forum2003/HenriPeakGage-Discharge-Precip.pdf |format=PDF |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928184512/http://ag.udel.edu/dwrc/newsletters/Forum2003/HenriPeakGage-Discharge-Precip.pdf }}</ref>。风暴对这些地区的影响还因接下来一周里来袭的[[飓风伊莎贝尔|飓风伊莎贝尔]]而严重加剧。
