9月6日，一股强劲东风波离开非洲海岸，并且几乎立即就与广阔的表面环流关联起来<ref name="td14tcr">{{cite web | last = Franklin | first = James | date = 2003-09-11 | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen Tropical Cyclone Report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714223740/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003fourteen.shtml | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003fourteen.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。受有利的上层风影响，系统组织结构迅速改善<ref>{{cite report | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | date = 2003-09-07 | title = September 7 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，于9月8日在佛得角群岛最南端的东南方向约465公里洋面发展成第十四号热带低气压<ref name="td14tcr" />。低气压起初未能保持深层对流组成的内核，形成位置附近还存在干燥空气，但美国国家飓风中心还是认为气旋所处环境有利于发展，可以达到飓风强度<ref name="td14disc1">{{cite web | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | date = 2003-09-08 | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-04-07 | archivedate = 2014-08-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al142003.discus.001.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812110957/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al142003.discus.001.shtml }}</ref>。

形成仅数小时后，低气压中心附近的对流就已消亡，带状特征也已消散<ref>{{cite web | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | date = 2003-09-08 | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen Discussion Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140812110908/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al142003.discus.002.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-04-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al142003.discus.002.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-08-12 }}</ref>。低气压上空的干燥空气有大幅增加，到了9月9日，国家飓风中心已认为气旋不会达到热带风暴的最低标准<ref>{{cite web | author = Knabb, Richard & Franklin, James | date = 2003-09-09 | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen Discussion Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-04-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150213083311/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al142003.discus.003.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al142003.discus.003.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-02-13 }}</ref>。当晚，有上层低气压南下到达系统西侧，导致风切变增多，并使系统向西北偏北稳步前进。途经佛得角群岛以西近海期间，气旋中的环流变得拉长，并与对流分隔开来<ref name="td14tcr" />，虽然给群岛带去暴雨<ref>{{cite web | last = Avila | first = Lixion | date = 2003-09-10 | title = Tropical Depression Fourteen Public Advisory Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-04-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/pub/al142003.public.008.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150213034332/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/pub/al142003.public.008.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-02-13 }}</ref>，但系统9月10日便已消散<ref name="td14tcr" />。
