{{Main|2003年热带风暴拉里}}
9月17日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开[[非洲|非洲]]西海岸，于9月27日在加勒比海西部发展出低气压区。9月29日，系统沿尤卡坦半岛登岸，并因与基本保持静止的锋面天气系统相互影响而发展成温带气旋。随着深层对流增多，系统于10月1日转变成热带风暴拉里。风暴总体向南飘移，在达到风力时速100公里的最高强度后于10月5日登陆墨西哥[[塔巴斯科州|塔巴斯科州]]<ref name="larrytcr">{{cite web | author = Stacy Stuart | year = 2003 | title = Tropical Storm Larry Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002000226/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003larry.shtml | accessdate = 2013-10-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003larry.shtml | archivedate = 2013-10-02 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，成为1973年的[[1973年飓风布伦达|热带风暴布伦达]]以来首场登陆该州的风暴<ref name="mexgob">{{cite web |author=Servicio Meteorológico Nacional |year=2003 |title=Tormenta Tropical "Larry" del Océano Atlántico |accessdate=2015-04-04 |archivedate=2014-10-06 |deadurl=yes |url=http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2003/atlantico/larry/larry.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006073719/http://smn.cna.gob.mx/ciclones/tempo2003/atlantico/larry/larry.html }}</ref>。拉里的残留穿过[[特万特佩克地峡|特万特佩克地峡]]，逐渐退化成残留低气压区，最终于10月7日在东太平洋逐渐消散<ref name="larrytcr" />。

拉里降下暴雨，墨西哥东南部的上华雷斯（{{lang|en|Upper Juarez}}）降雨量最高，达629.2毫米<ref name="larain">{{cite web | author = David Roth | year = 2006 | title = Rainfall data for Tropical Storm Larry | publisher = HPC | accessdate = 2015-04-04 | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006081610/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/larry2003.html | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/larry2003.html }}</ref>。降雨引发多场[[泥石流|泥石流]]并造成破坏，这其中还有东太平洋[[2003年飓风诺拉|热带低气压诺拉]]和[[2003年飓风奥拉夫|热带风暴奥拉夫]]的影响<ref name="aplar">{{cite news | author = Lorena Moguel, Associated Press Writer | year = 2003 | title = Tropical Depression Olaf weakens after moving inland | accessdate = 2015-04-04 | url = http://airwolf.lmtonline.com/news/archive/100903/pagea12.pdf | archivedate = 2015-04-04 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150404151154/http://airwolf.lmtonline.com/news/archive/100903/pagea12.pdf }}</ref>。拉里一共造成5人丧生<ref name="larrytcr" />，经济损失达5360万美元（2003年[[美元|美元]]，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|53600000|2003}}}}美元）<ref name="zuniga">{{cite web | author = Foro Consultivo Cientifico y Technológio | year = 2005 | title = Desastres mayores registrados en México de 1980 a 2003 | accessdate = 2015-04-04 | format = PDF | archivedate = 2012-02-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120204170201/http://www.foroconsultivo.org.mx/eventos_realizados/proteccion1/ponencias/zuniga.pdf | url = http://www.foroconsultivo.org.mx/eventos_realizados/proteccion1/ponencias/zuniga.pdf | deadurl = no }}</ref>。
