10月1日，一股东风波离开非洲海岸向西移动<ref name="mtcr">{{cite web | last = Lawrence | first = Miles | year = 2003 | title = Tropical Storm Mindy Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-10-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003mindy.shtml? | archivedate = 2013-10-02 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002000235/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003mindy.shtml }}</ref>。10月8日，小安的列斯群岛各地都出现雷雨天气，东风波也缓慢组织<ref name="oct8two">{{cite report | last = Beven | first = Jack | date = 2003-10-08 | title = October 8 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。[[圣克洛伊岛|圣克洛伊岛]]的[[克里斯琴斯特德|克里斯琴斯特德]]降雨量达到75毫米，[[龐塞|龐塞]]附近更有181毫米<ref name="mindyrain">{{cite web | author = David Roth | year = 2005 | title = Rainfall Information for Tropical Storm Mindy | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2015-04-07 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/mindy2003.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130922025041/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/mindy2003.html | archivedate = 2013-09-22 }}</ref>。[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]东北部有约2万9000人失去供电<ref name="ncdc6">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2003 | title = Event Report for Puerto Rico (6) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。降水破坏了[[拉斯彼德拉斯_(波多黎各)|拉斯彼德拉斯]]和[[瓜亞馬|瓜亞馬]]的多座桥梁<ref name="ncdc8">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2003 | title = Event Report for Puerto Rico (8) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref><ref name="ncdc12">{{cite web | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2003 | title = Event Report for Puerto Rico (12) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，还引起河流泛滥、树木倒霉，有4条道路因岩崩封闭。一辆汽车被水卷走<ref name="ncdc3">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2003 | title = Event Report for Puerto Rico (3) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，还有少量房屋被淹<ref name="ncdc4">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2003 | title = Event Report for Puerto Rico (4) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，总计经济损失至少有4万6000美元（2003年[[美元|美元]]，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|46000|2003}}}}美元）<ref name="ncdc8" /><ref name="ncdc12" /><ref name="ncdc11">{{cite report | author = National Climatic Data Center | year = 2003 | title = Event Report for Puerto Rico (11) | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。

系统转向西北，从副热带高压脊的薄弱点通过，虽受强烈风切变的不利影响，但还是于10月10日在多明尼加东部上空发展成热带风暴明迪，达到的最高风速为每小时75公里<ref name="mtcr" />。[[聖地亞哥-羅里蓋茲省|聖地亞哥-羅里蓋茲省]]的降雨量为60毫米，引起洪灾并导致320套房屋受损<ref name="wmo" />。美国国家飓风中心一度预测明迪的风速会达到每小时105公里，但气旋实际上由于风切变影响而减弱<ref name="mindydisc2">{{cite web | author = Beven | year = 2003 | title = Tropical Storm Mindy Discussion Two | publisher = NHC | accessdate = 2015-04-08 | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024203538/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al182003.discus.002.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2003/dis/al182003.discus.002.shtml? }}</ref>。风暴中心于10月11日从[[特克斯和凯科斯群岛|特克斯和凯科斯群岛]]附近经过<ref name="mtcr" />，[[大特克島|大特克島]]上的风速只达到每小时50公里<ref name="wmo">{{cite web | author = World Meteorological Organization | year = 2004 | title = Final Report of the 2003 Hurricane Season | accessdate = 2014-03-18 | archivedate = 2013-11-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131104140940/http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/documents/HC26-English.pdf | url = http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/documents/HC26-English.pdf | format = PDF }}</ref>。10月12日，明迪降级成热带低气压，之后因短波[[低壓槽|槽]]逼近而转朝东面前进。深层对流消亡后，系统环流于10月14日在[[百慕大|百慕大]]西南编南方向约715公里洋面消散<ref name="mtcr" />。明迪给佛罗里达州到北卡罗莱纳州之间的美国东海岸带去了0.6至0.9米的涌浪<ref name="surfline" />。

