{{main|2003年热带风暴奥德特}}
热带风暴奥德特于12月4日在加勒比海西南部形成，是继1984年的[[1984年飓风丽丽|飓风丽丽]]以来首场在12月形成的热带风暴。奥德特的强度有所提高，于12月6日以中等热带风暴强度从法尔索角（{{lang|es|Cabo Falso}}）附近登陆多明尼加共和国。一天后，风暴转变成温带气旋，最终与冷锋融合<ref name="odettetcr">{{cite web | last = Franklin | first = James | date = 2003-12-19 | title = Tropical Storm Odette Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-10-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003odette.shtml? | archivedate = 2013-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002000253/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2003odette.shtml | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

气旋在多明尼加引起泥石流和山洪爆发，直接导致8人遇难，还间接造成两人丧生，该国35%的[[香蕉|香蕉]]作物毁于一旦<ref name="odettetcr" />。此外，波多黎各还出现小到中雨<ref name="wpc2">{{cite web | last = Roth | first = David | date = 2007-06-20 | title = Tropical Storm Odette - December 3-7, 2003 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2015-04-08 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/odette2003.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150404184503/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/odette2003.html | archivedate = 2015-04-04 }}</ref>。
